Package: portalr
Title: Create useful summaries of the Portal data
Version: 0.1.0
Maintainer: Glenda M. Yenni <glenda@weecology.org>
Author:     Glenda M. Yenni [aut],
    Ellen K. Bledsoe [aut],
    Erica M. Christensen [aut],
    Renata M. Diaz [aut],
    S.K. Morgan Ernest [aut, cre],
    Juniper L. Simonis [aut],
    Shawn D. Taylor [aut],
    Ethan P. White [aut],
    Hao Ye [aut]
Description: This package contains functions for downloading the latest 
    version of the Portal data and to generate summaries of the rodent, 
    plant, ant, and weather data. 
License: MIT
URL: https://github.com/weecology/portalr
BugReports: https://github.com/weecology/portalr/issues
LazyData: true
